        <div class='post__title__excerpt wysiwyg p italic mb1 mt025 pr2 o4 theme__text ' >
            In this episode of The Joy of Why, Thomas Hertog discusses his collaboration with Stephen Hawking on a provocative theory arguing that the laws of physics evolved with the universe, and how this could have shaped a cosmos fit for life.        </div>
